'''生物医学（{{lang-en|Biomedical sciences or Biomedicine}}）'''是医学的分支，负责将[[生物技术|生物技术]]和其他[[自然科学|自然科学]]理论应用于[[临床实践|临床实践]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.memidex.com/biomedicine+applies-biological-physiological |title=biomedicine (applies biological, physiological) - Memidex dictionary/thesaurus |work=memidex.com |date=2012-10-08 |accessdate=2012-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191017144519/http://www.memidex.com/biomedicine+applies-biological-physiological |archive-date=2019-10-17 |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 生物医学主要运用[[生物学|生物学]]和[[生理学|生理学]]的知识。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thefreedictionary.com/biomedical|title=biomedicine - The Free Dictionary|year=2013|accessdate=2013-05-15|archive-date=2021-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210323233656/https://www.thefreedictionary.com/biomedical|dead-url=no}}</ref>

生物医学与[[健康|健康]]和生物学相关领域有关联，并且从上世纪以来一直在健康系统中扮演着重要的角色。<ref>Medicine's paradigm shift: An opportunity for psychologyBy Dr. Suzanne Bennett Johnson, APA PresidentSeptember 2012, Vol 43, No. 8Print version: page 5, [http://www.apa.org/monitor/2012/09/pc.aspx] {{Wayback|url=http://www.apa.org/monitor/2012/09/pc.aspx |date=20201011205505 }}</ref><ref>Do biomedical models of illness make for good healthcare systems?BMJ 2004; 329, 09 December 2004, [http://www.bmj.com/content/329/7479/1398] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bmj.com/content/329/7479/1398 |date=20210218020239 }}</ref><ref>The Need for a New Medical Model: A Challenge for BiomedicineAuthor(s): George L. EngelSource: Science, New Series, Vol. 196, No. 4286 (Apr. 8, 1977), pp. 129-136, [http://www.drannejensen.com/PDF/publications/The%20need%20for%20a%20new%20medical%20model%20-%20A%20challenge%20for%20biomedicine.pdf] {{Wayback|url=http://www.drannejensen.com/PDF/publications/The%20need%20for%20a%20new%20medical%20model%20-%20A%20challenge%20for%20biomedicine.pdf |date=20200921055356 }}</ref><ref>Vital Notes for Nurses: Principles of Care By Hilary Lloyd, Helen Hancock, Steven Campbell, p. 6, [https://books.google.com/books?id=02pQLW24ncIC&pg=PA6&lpg=PA6&dq=The+biomedical+model+of+illness,+which+has+dominated+health+care+for+the+past+century&source=bl&ots=J34Ls1kCmb&sig=gd6zEM0ShkZ6TV1ImNquW_mcDs4&hl=en&sa=X&ei=TV1wVZLLKoaOyAShgIPoCQ&ved=0CDwQ6AEwBA#v=snippet&q=%22biomedical%20model%22&f=false] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=02pQLW24ncIC&pg=PA6&lpg=PA6&dq=The+biomedical+model+of+illness,+which+has+dominated+health+care+for+the+past+century&source=bl&ots=J34Ls1kCmb&sig=gd6zEM0ShkZ6TV1ImNquW_mcDs4&hl=en&sa=X&ei=TV1wVZLLKoaOyAShgIPoCQ&ved=0CDwQ6AEwBA#v=snippet&q=%22biomedical%20model%22&f=false |date=20201011205519 }}</ref>  

==生物醫學領域==
生物医学有许多的分支学科和专业领域，其名称通常以“生物-”（bio-）开头，如：

* [[分子生物学|分子生物学]]，[[生物化学|生物化学]]，[[生物技术|生物技术]]，[[细胞生物学|细胞生物学]] [[胚胎学|胚胎学]]，
* {{le|纳米生物技术|Nanobiotechnology}}，[[生物工程|生物工程]]，[[实验室医学生物学|实验室医学生物学]]， 
* [[细胞遗传学|细胞遗传学]]，[[遗传学|遗传学]]，[[基因疗法|基因疗法]]
* [[生物信息学|生物信息学]]，[[生物统计学|生物统计学]]，[[系统生物学|系统生物学]]，
* [[微生物学|微生物学]]，[[病毒学|病毒学]]，[[寄生虫学|寄生虫学]] 
* [[生理学|生理学]]，[[病理学|病理学]]，
* [[毒理学|药理毒理学]]，许多人认为[[生命科学|生命科学]]可以应用于[[医学|医学]]。

